headline: CoStar Group Sets the Record Straight on Matterport Spaces
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., October 22, 2025--CoStar Group, Inc. (NASDAQ: CSGP), a leading provider of online real estate marketplaces, information, analytics, and 3D digital twin technology, announced its continued support for Matterport Spaces across all media channels.
